Majandra Delfino https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Majandra_Delfino 0 Majandra Delfino (born February 20, 1981) is an American actress and singer. An Alma Award-winner, she is best known for her role as Maria DeLuca on Roswell, and as Andi on the CBS multi-cam Friends With Better Lives.
